        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"},
          "expr": "sum by (source_type) (grace_ingestion_runs_failed_total{source_type=~\"$source_type\"})",
          "legendFormat": "failed {{source_type}}",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Per-Source Run Health",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"},
      "description": "Voice & Tone profile generation rate (D428).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never"},
          "noValue": "No data yet"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8},
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["sum"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "single", "sort": "none"}
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"},
          "expr": "rate(grace_voice_tone_profiles_generated_total[$__rate_interval])",
          "legendFormat": "profiles/s",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Profile Generation Rate",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"},
      "description": "Re-triage rescue rate. For detailed stats, see GET /api/ingestion/retriage/stats and Chunk 59 retriage_rescue structlog events.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"noValue": "See /api/ingestion/retriage/stats for detailed re-triage metrics."},
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8},
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "code": {"language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false},
        "content": "## Re-triage Rescue Rate\n\nRe-triage rescues are tracked via structlog events (`retriage_rescue`) and the REST API:\n\n- `GET /api/ingestion/retriage/stats` — latest cycle, total filtered, by-state breakdown.\n- Chunk 59 `retriage_rescue` structlog events in application logs.\n\nNo Prometheus metric for re-triage in Chunk 61 scope.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Re-triage Rescue Rate",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"},
